				I am a barbarian warrior of the 6th Level and I had stopped into the bar where Tumpy hangs out to turn in some Moonstones to the bartender (see quests in Qeynos) when I saw Tumpy at the bar.  I talked to him, bought him some Mead Ale that he asked for and then asked him questions about the people he mentioned.  When I brought up S'ragg (sp?) he said, &quot;Where did you hear that name, not from me..&quot; and left the bar in a huff.  I followed him and since he conned blue to me, I attacked him down one of the streets and managed to kill him.  Now, I am not a twink.  All the armor I was wearing was patchwork that I had made and the weapon I was using was a rusty halberd that I looted off of a skeleton I had killed.  None of Tumpy's friends joined in and I managed to steer the fight away from the guards.  I now have his head and am going to head to Kaladim - it is a long run though.  Any kindly spellcasters want to help out a young warrior with a teleport?
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
